questions.question:
How many times does this loop iterate?

int i = 0;
while (i < 3) {
    System.out.println(i);
    i++;
}

What values does this loop print?

int i = 10;
while (i > 0) {
    System.out.println(i);
    i--;
}

In this loop, what is the initialization?

int count = 1;
while (count <= 5) {
    System.out.println(count);
    count++;
}

What happens after this loop finishes?

int countdown = 5;
while (countdown > 0) {
    System.out.println(countdown);
    countdown--;
}
System.out.println("Liftoff!");

In this loop, what is the update?

int temperature = 60;
while (temperature < 70) {
    System.out.println(temperature);
    temperature += 2;
}
